title: Ep. 139 - Antifa is a Terrorist Group
description:
Should the media stop naming mass killers? Also, left-wing thugs descend on Tucker Carlson's house. Why don't police treat them like the terrorists they are? Finally, I wrote an innocuous tweet and someone said my house should burn down because of it. What does that say about the state of discourse in America? Date: 11-08-2018
